item.description:
We will start with a half hour of social or unstructured time.

Then I will spend a few minutes thanking all of you for making the weekend a success for the campaign.

We will then concentrate on 2 or 3 efforts/projects for the immediate future - including raising money for Ron Paul.

If there is interest in having two or three parallel meetings (simultaneously or otherwise) to help us organize our projects, we shall consider it at this meeting.

Signs have arrived. Bumper stickers are here. Slim Jims are available (here)

Go Ron Paul!
